    <item>
      <title>阿联酋领导人下令在创纪录降雨后进行损失评估</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uae-leader-orders-damage-assessment-after-record-rainfall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉伯联合酋长国将评估本周早些时候袭击该国的严重风暴对其基础设施造成的损害，该风暴淹没了重要的高速公路并扰乱了迪拜主要机场的运营。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uae-leader-orders-damage-assessment-after-record-rainfall</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 06:34:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
